description: "These three maps are marked with shoals, rocks, water depth, safe entry points, and anchorage locations, to help ships safely anchor. The sites include the Joseph Freewill Islands (Mapia Atoll, Indonesia) and the coast of Mindanao in the Philippines."
title: "A   dangerous   shoal   seen   Septr.   the   28,   1767   (Joseph   Freewills   Islands)"
